{
  "chapter": 4,
  "chapter_summary": "本章讲述杨华在石林苦练武功一年，研习孟家刀法和崆峒派武学。他发现刀法注解竟是母亲云紫萝的笔迹，百思不得其解。之后杨华发现剑峰上的张丹枫密室，获得《玄功要诀》和\"无名剑法\"十八式。在准备离开石林时，他偶遇一男一女闯入石林，男子自称段家后人（段青），女子被称为冰妹。两人是来寻找段青的叔叔段仇世，并打听孟元超和小金川义军的消息。杨华悄悄跟踪偷听，得知许多关于孟元超和段仇世的信息。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "那少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里真是神仙洞府！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_qing",
      "speaker_name": "那男的",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你可别忘记留下记号，要是找不着我的叔父，咱们出去，可就难了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "那少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你放心，我不会忘记的。我来此的时候，孟大侠早已叮嘱过我了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_qing",
      "speaker_name": "那男的",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "孟元超是我叔父的好朋友，可我还没有见过他呢。冰妹，你怎的知道应该向他打听消息的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_mei",
      "speaker_name": "那少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "青哥，你怎的如此糊涂，自己说过的话也都忘了？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_qing",
      "speaker_name": "那男的",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，我记起来了。有一次咱们谈论当今豪杰，我是曾向你提过我的叔父和孟元超的交情。那次咱们谈论的人很多，在场的也还有别人，想不到已经过了一年多了，你还记得。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_mei",
      "speaker_name": "那少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说过的话，每一句我都记得！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_qing",
      "speaker_name": "那男的",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "冰妹，你真细心。可是，唉，糟糕！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_mei",
      "speaker_name": "那少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么糟糕？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_qing",
      "speaker_name": "那男的",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你这样细心，以后我可不敢在你跟前说错一句话了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_mei",
      "speaker_name": "那少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知道就好。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_qing",
      "speaker_name": "那男的",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱们还是说正经的吧，孟大侠是怎样和你说的？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_mei",
      "speaker_name": "那少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不是已经告诉过你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_qing",
      "speaker_name": "那男的",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我想知道详细一些。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_mei",
      "speaker_name": "那少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，那我再说一遍。或许那天我说的有什么遗漏。要是你听不明白，还可以问我。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_qing",
      "speaker_name": "那男的",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也想知道更多一些有关孟元超、令师叔以及小金川义军的事情。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_mei",
      "speaker_name": "那少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好的，我尽我所知，说与你听就是。先说你叔父的事情。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 269,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_mei",
      "speaker_name": "那少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "令叔最后一次见到孟大侠的时候，曾经告诉他是准备前往石林。据说是要找一位朋友。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_qing",
      "speaker_name": "那男的",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知他找的是什么朋友？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_mei",
      "speaker_name": "那少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他没有告诉孟大侠。不过，你是他的侄儿，他的朋友，你大概也应知道一些吧。想一想看。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_qing",
      "speaker_name": "那男的",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不知道，我的叔叔当年是因为和我爹爹不和而出走的，直到我二十岁的时候，他方才回来一趟，我跟他出去，没多久又分手了。他的朋友，我知道的只有孟元超和缪长风，另外就是他死去的师兄卜天雕了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 285,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_mei",
      "speaker_name": "那少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来如此。不过，这石林的主人既然是你叔叔的朋友，想必不是坏人。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_qing",
      "speaker_name": "那男的",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那是一年多的事情了，叔叔不知是否还在这儿？咱们进来这许久，仍没发现人迹。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_mei",
      "speaker_name": "那少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在这个好像八阵图的石林之中，你是不是有点害怕了？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 293,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_qing",
      "speaker_name": "那男的",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "即使有甚危险，我也还是要来的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_mei",
      "speaker_name": "那少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有一句话，不知我该不该问你。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_qing",
      "speaker_name": "那男的",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你对我是知无不言，我岂能瞒你。你尽管问吧。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_mei",
      "speaker_name": "那少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我看你好像另外还有什么心事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_qing",
      "speaker_name": "那男的",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你真厉害，心事也瞒不过你。不错，我此来固然是为了寻找叔叔，另外却也还有一件事情。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_mei",
      "speaker_name": "那少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事情？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_qing",
      "speaker_name": "那男的",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这石林和我段家大有关系。不过，现在我还没看见剑池剑峰，要是找到了那个地方，我再告诉你吧。",
      "tone": "神秘",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 311
    }
  ],
